HEADWORD: Clarifier
<hw>Clar"i*fi`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>That
which clarifies.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A vessel in which the process of clarification is
conducted; <as>as, the <ex>clarifier</ex> in sugar works</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Ure.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

